{"tid":1845763,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇胡志明同吳廷琰兩個越南獨裁者都咁專一？","createTime":"2020-01-27T10:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T11:36:31.000Z","uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9f04aad300e2c41e97cdde6cde6aecc3f4a1f659","tid":1845763,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"胡志明在中國時，娶了一位中國妻子－曾雪明，但是對於這一段異國婚姻，越南官方絕口不認，反而將深情的胡志明，塑造成一個不談情愛的愛國革命家。<br />\n<br />\n吳廷琰一生中僅有一次戀愛：他愛上了老師的一位女兒，但由於那位女性出家成為修女，所以終身不娶。"},{"pid":"0bffd83ebb58fdcc0a500a28faba93e3e1e229ad","tid":1845763,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:36:48.000Z","msg":"因為大家都係越南人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30699d112ea4e9687ffaf59ca81030e6738f301","tid":1845763,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f8e241333bbf9ef2e05b820f1e2a64b8c0ab45","tid":1845763,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}